skos:Concept.skos:scopeNote: {"id": "d83b369b-d7f9-4ca2-9433-6cafbbf4971c", "value": "Any harm that can be attributed to the effects of recreational activities on a population or its habitat. (This can include camping, hiking, shooting, hunting, team games, etc.)"}

{"id": "4b46dbd8-a42b-4aa9-8af3-beeb3656c3ac", "value": "The selective removal of trees and/or bushes from an area usually on a smaller scale than logging. Often associated with collecting firewood or brush removal for fire control. Also includes \u00d2fuels modification projects\u00d3 performed by the Forest Service."}

{"id": "a3798557-2370-4429-82b5-36c6c2c5beeb", "value": "Any threat that can not be reasonably assigned to an existing threat code (ex. powerline projects, border patrol activities, habitat fragmentation)."}
{"id": "42eb091b-e4df-4764-8793-86d9bffebc58", "value": "Degradation of water quality that is the result of human activities."}
{"id": "c119b435-ae3d-4b05-b214-2d4b528a6ee9", "value": "Reduction in the quality of a population due to mixing of genetic material."}

{"id": "faab1b3c-2718-4f96-b323-5f33ac1c69a4", "value": "The size of the population is small enough that it could easily be extirpated due to chance events and/or experience genetic bottlenecks, inbreeding depression, etc."}

{"id": "b3f5d77a-16e5-4875-aea3-7653bc63c35e", "value": "Any activity that turns or loosens the soil (usually done by farm equipment) in preparation for planting or sowing of seeds (includes tilling and plowing)."}
{"id": "6f870ce5-65f5-4631-9313-e290b3dee519", "value": "Damage associated with the presence and activities of feral (wild) pigs."}

{"id": "e9b80f88-0104-4583-8ccb-ec1bdf47a169", "value": "The alteration of the natural fire cycle of an area usually due to fire suppression or prescribed burning, but also including increases in fire frequency (such as in southern California)."}
{"id": "522e0bfc-1e82-4d98-8909-1bfe71d244d2", "value": "Reduction in the quality of habitat and/or population due to the presence of non-native plant species."}

{"id": "73c47d06-a352-4134-8789-3ae6d7127486", "value": "Elimination or alteration of habitat due to the construction of a dam or berm (includes excessive water flow resulting in scouring & inundation of stream channels)."}
{"id": "d48a806a-d126-4abb-adca-3f47982baab2", "value": "Removal of trees on a larger scale, generally by logging companies and agencies (including US Forest Service). Also see Woodcutting below."}
{"id": "ecaae48f-c350-4443-8057-f784bf774df9", "value": "A change in the temperature of a habitat, such as the removal of riparian\u00cavegetation which results in an increased stream temperature."}

{"id": "727916b5-79e7-4f8d-88a9-c7334d48c060", "value": "Activities performed by the military that may negatively affect an area. (This can include tank maneuvers, the use of bombs and ordinance, off-road driving, troop training, etc.)"}

{"id": "35e0f586-dd20-42f0-bc0a-1c7b98e82958", "value": "Protection or maintenance of the banks of a river/stream/body of water resulting in the elimination or degradation of sensitive species habitat (includes levee maintenance and the use of riprap)."}
{"id": "1f5dd285-a594-4eca-8415-387a4591ed0e", "value": "The trampling or disturbance of an area due to human or animal foot traffic. (This can include trampling by cows such as in vernal pools.)"}

{"id": "2d6386e3-55a8-4fea-82e5-57a2d342c510", "value": "Any alteration to the pre-existing hydrology or water flow in an area which negatively affects a species. Also see Dam/Inundation and Surface water diversion below."}
{"id": "ba31ee12-ee6f-4f30-8056-fc1c3c239bc6", "value": "Construction of houses, businesses, parks, etc. resulting in elimination/degradation of natural/native habitat."}
{"id": "d7c05781-b534-4ccd-bac8-232869d0aafa", "value": "Contamination of an area with pollutants."}
{"id": "c7596976-ac15-4375-96ea-27fc7a9ebebe", "value": "Reduction in the quality of a population due to the presence of disease."}
{"id": "e3a007d8-5a92-4070-93b4-ae84ef9342c5", "value": "Any damage associated with motorized vehicles going off of designated roads."}
{"id": "ef754b8f-7e85-4258-b8a5-0106ee54d171", "value": "Negative impacts associated with the use of herbicides and/or pesticides."}
{"id": "a43b15da-311b-40aa-9a9b-35920dc2aa24", "value": "Impacts related to the grazing of livestock. (This can include cattle, sheep, goats, horses, etc.)"}
{"id": "f5b169f2-a250-4525-bf9b-3808195edd28", "value": "Negative impacts associated with an animal laying its eggs in another animal's nest"}
{"id": "53977a6f-767f-4a32-8e9f-a7bd5a311f7a", "value": "Disturbance of an area due to the construction or maintenance of roads (including highways/freeways) or trails."}
{"id": "aff67a85-9fe9-41d1-a425-01f54e3755ca", "value": "Elimination of habitat or other adverse impacts due to agricultural development or agriculture-related activities. Also see Biocides below."}
{"id": "0b7e6196-16d9-43d0-b531-941d0caede57", "value": "Death of an animal resulting from collisions with, or being driven over by, a vehicle."}
{"id": "839b19b3-42a7-4aa8-9cb4-b0c57609ba9a", "value": "The alteration of the natural flow and meandering of a river or stream by straightening its course."}
{"id": "bcd4879b-665d-432b-8dc3-0740c87debbc", "value": "Lowering of the water table due to the pumping/removal of groundwater."}

{"id": "504b3dcf-463a-40c8-a75a-a79023a21b88", "value": "Competition with, damage from, & predation by non-native animals, excluding feral pigs and livestock. (Use threat code 34 for feral pig damage & threat code 4 for livestock damage.)"}
{"id": "3e611607-8f13-4dd5-ba60-c949f469ff02", "value": "Death of an animal resulting from collisions with wind turbines, radio/electrical towers, power lines, or other man-made structures."}

{"id": "bc58a744-c80f-49cf-8837-3079ad0affc9", "value": "When a population is threatened by, or a habitat degraded by, erosion activities or (usually) polluted runoff. This can include erosion due to wave action, such as in the Delta."}
{"id": "db7fbdb6-f35d-4718-a73d-487efad48417", "value": "Collection of plants or animals, or poaching of animals, which has detrimental effects on the population."}
{"id": "dcf469a5-cd29-47cb-b73b-413f31f2ddcb", "value": "Elimination/degradation of habitat due to the construction of a landfill or dump."}
{"id": "c942a51e-e08e-413b-b377-99aebf4124d4", "value": "Degradation/alteration of habitat due to mining activities\u00ca."}
{"id": "bebced80-c74f-4077-b84b-c101a7b5a266", "value": "Diversion of water to another area, or draining of water, resulting in the disruption of the natural surface water flow in an area."}
{"id": "d6c4933a-c9b6-4050-8d4a-09fa716d3bab", "value": "Damage or destruction of a plant/animal or their associated habitat due to vandalism or trash dumping."}
